alert.note: Alert for Eastern Alaska Range North of Trims Camp (Alaska) Issued by the National Weather Service

info.headline: High Wind Warning issued November 28 at 1:51PM AKST until November 29 at 6:00AM AKST by NWS Fairbanks
info.description: ...HIGH WIND WARNING REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 AM AKST WEDNESDAY... * WHAT...South winds 50 mph with gusts up to 75 mph expected. * WHERE...Eastern Alaska Range North of Trims Camp. * WHEN...Until 6 AM AKST Wednesday. * IMPACTS...Strong winds may blow down trees and power lines. Power outages are possible. Travel will be difficult, especially for high profile vehicles. * ADDITIONAL DETAILS...The highest winds are expected this evening and late tonight. Winds will decrease Wednesday morning.
info.instruction: People should avoid being outside in forested areas and around trees and branches. Use caution if you must drive.
